            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
                        
                        <p>Yes, it&rsquo;s true that America is the land of opportunity, the land where all things are possible. We&rsquo;re a country where people can dream big dreams and if we they try hard enough, we can accomplish them. We&rsquo;re a country that values equal opportunity and the importance of basic human rights. But sadly, we&rsquo;re also a country that often forgets just how lucky we are to have such good fortune.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Anne Katharine Wales is a Trinity junior.</p>

